You are my sunshine. My whole heart. My everything.🤍☀️
.
.
.
.
.
.
.
Love IG stories & wanted to put together some of my favs to look back on.💗✨

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Living My Best Style // Katy R on July 07, 2021. May be a closeup of 1 person.

node.text: Heyyy… I went brunette.👍🏼🤣 Also, got a new bra I’m obsessed with, read a new book- When We Believed In Mermaids🧜🏽‍♀️, & took a few days off work. Heck ya!!💃🏼⭐️ It’s the little things!!👏🏼

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by Living My Best Style // Katy R on July 03, 2021 tagging @pinklily. May be an image of 1 person and outdoors.

node.text:
Hey Alexa, set timer for ‘VACATION’☀️🌺 Fam bam is here & I’m taking off the gram’ for a few days! WOOHOO! (It’s been three years since I’ve put this little app down- whattt🤯) I will miss you guys but wishing you all a happy & safe July 4th, peace, & blessings!💛💛 

I made rum infused pineapple, pasta salad, ice cream coffee pie & it’s supposed to be a beautiful 80° week!✨👋🏼

See ya in a few days, gals!👯‍♀️💗 
.
.
.
.
Pic is old: Bathing suit is from my @pinklily line which is sadly sold out! But I’m linking up a few items I just ordered two night ago!! Code: KATY20 for 20% off!💗💗💗
